{"tid":2095842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想走，但係我想生細路","createTime":"2020-07-05T18:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T12:27:42.000Z","uid":198514,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a6d1ab65ac17ab2abe0d03c01583fbb630ddb3b7","tid":2095842,"uid":198514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:44:59.000Z","msg":"我想建立自己家庭，有小朋友<br />\n所以要走<br />\n<br />\n我唔係介意留低抗爭<br />\n一齊 做暴民 打共匪<br />\n但係一諗到個仔將來d同學係蝗<br />\n返學講蝗語玩抖音<br />\n大衛貝克漢姆<br />\n我會好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果香港人大家都願意留低生仔<br />\n起碼個仔講廣東話成長<br />\n就算做mk仔都好過做的士陳<br />\n咁我都會留低<br />\n<br />\n不過而家大部分人都去第d地方先諗生仔<br />\n留底？不了"},{"pid":"00aba2e8695e0039494859db3538d0127c8ea987","tid":2095842,"uid":361753,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:48:55.000Z","msg":"你望下依家啲小學生先，講匪語，睇抖音。啲價值觀跟撚晒大陸。樓豬夢要醒了，舊香港已回不去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdefa7521a0edc32faad141d53e66c2bab9b5ee1","tid":2095842,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:52:45.000Z","msg":"而家連中學生都睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71172ac4e492afdae7a6d153fda27a50eab5f7c","tid":2095842,"uid":198514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00aba2e8695e0039494859db3538d0127c8ea987","tid":2095842,"uid":361753,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:48:55.000Z","msg":"你望下依家啲小學生先，講匪語，睇抖音。啲價值觀跟撚晒大陸。樓豬夢要醒了，舊香港已回不去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:59:22.000Z","msg":"一早醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真心想抗爭，係咪選擇左留低就唔好再諗組家庭？<br 